nodes.bodyText:
A couple of comments:

Why include the server name twice in the hash?  Given that we've already salted the hash using the server name, we can just use:

md.digest(service.getInstanceId().getBytes(StandardCharsets.UTF-8));

Given that we don't know the default character encoding of a given host, it's probably best to keep this consistent across all hosts, e.g.

String encodedRoute = new String(encoder.encode(...), StandardCharsets.UTF-8);

